<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Password Berhasil Diubah</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 24px;
      background-color: #f2f4f8;
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #1f2937;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .wrapper {
      max-width: 620px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .card {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.07);
    }
    .header {
      padding: 24px 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #166534 0%, #16a34a 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .brand {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.2px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 28px;
    }
    .title {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #0f172a;
    }
    p {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .notice {
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 0 0 16px;
    }
    .notice.success {
      background-color: #f0fdf4;
      border: 1px solid #86efac;
      color: #166534;
    }
    .notice.warning {
      background-color: #fff7ed;
      border: 1px solid #fdba74;
      color: #9a3412;
    }
    .meta {
      margin: 16px 0;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .meta-row {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 0 28px 24px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #64748b;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="header">
        <p class="brand">{{companyName}}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h1 class="title">Password Berhasil Diubah</h1>

        <p>Halo {{name}},</p>

        <div class="notice success">Password akun Anda berhasil diperbarui.</div>

        <p>Berikut detail perubahan terbaru pada akun Anda:</p>
        <div class="meta">
          <p class="meta-row"><strong>Waktu:</strong> {{changedAt}}</p>
          <p class="meta-row"><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{ipAddress}}</p>
          <p class="meta-row"><strong>Perangkat:</strong> {{userAgent}}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="notice warning">
          Jika Anda tidak merasa melakukan perubahan ini, segera amankan akun Anda dan hubungi tim support.
        </div>

        <p>Untuk alasan keamanan, gunakan password baru Anda saat login berikutnya.</p>
        <p>Salam,<br>Tim {{companyName}}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>© {{year}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>Email ini dikirim otomatis, mohon tidak membalas.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
